name: CfaTestBank
overview:
For CFA candidates:

CfaTestBank.com is going to be launched in beta on 1st August 2009 and would provide following services:

  1. Test bank - thousands of questions prepared by experts, easily customizable.
  2. Compare your scores with others, share tests with friends, access them from your iPhone etc.
  3. Flash cards - learn in bits while on the go and remember the topics.
  4. **Most important - telephonic guidance

Avail very low priced premium membership right now and get instant access to telephonic guidance. After 1st August membership price will be doubled. If you are not satisfied with the service anytime then your money will be returned. Also if you don’t pass the exam then your money will be returned.

Contact at contact@cfatestbank.com

Checkout the space – CFA Test Bank http://www.CfaTestBank.com
